NAME
    Dancer::Plugin::TimeRequests - log how long each request took to process

DESCRIPTION
    A simple Dancer plugin to log how long each request took to process.
    Useful to examine performance.

    Future versions will likely add a stats page to show which routes take
    most time, etc.

SYNOPSIS
    In your Dancer app, load this module:

        use Dancer::Plugin::TimeRequests

    Then, when your app is logging in debug mode, log messages will be
    generated showing how logn each request look.

